<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Thanks for the question, @Cookie!! :D<br/><br/>At this point, there will (probably) be a sampler of TRUTHWITCH available on Netgalley/Edelweiss. It&apos;ll be a BIG <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Thanks for the question, @Cookie!! :D<br /><br />At this point, there will (probably) be a sampler of TRUTHWITCH available on Netgalley/Edelweiss. It'll be a BIG sampler (like 40% of the book and almost 200 pages), but piracy has become such an issue, publishers are doing more and more samplers instead of full e-galleys.<br /><br />There'll also be LOADS of giveaways between now and release! Via my Twitter( <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://twitter.com/stdennard">http://twitter.com/stdennard</a>), my newsletter (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://us3.campaign-archive1.com/home/?u=cdd0d036e9531dd416bf945b3&amp;id=11e0c331be">http://us3.campaign-archive1.com/home...</a>), and Goodreads!! So just stay tuned!! &lt;3<br /><br />Thanks for the question and the interest!! &lt;3<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
